title: Owls Split Again, Beat Green Mountain College (University of Maine at Presque Isle)
text: ( Source : University of Maine at Presque Isle ) LYNDONVILLE, VT - The University of Maine at Presque Isle defeated Green Mountain College 3-1, and then lost to host Lyndon State College 3-1 on Saturday. UMPI def. Green Mountain 3-1
